text: Calhoun County is the name of many counties in the United States, mostly named after Senator John C. Calhoun: * Calhoun County, Alabama * Calhoun County, Arkansas * Calhoun County, Florida * Calhoun County, Georgia * Calhoun County, Illinois * Calhoun County, Iowa * Calhoun County, Michigan * Calhoun County, Mississippi * Calhoun County, South Carolina * Calhoun County, Texas * Calhoun County, West Virginia
title: Calhoun County
